1:17:35.500 --> 1:17:36.875
And do you know why?

1:17:36.958 --> 1:17:38.791
'Cause it looks like we forgot.

1:17:38.875 --> 1:17:43.041
Times style is Times style,
and you are J-period R-period Maguire.

1:17:43.125 --> 1:17:45.041
Period.

1:17:45.125 --> 1:17:47.541
There's no periods after a last name.

1:17:47.625 --> 1:17:49.958
My congratulations on your fine work.

1:17:50.041 --> 1:17:52.250
You got a byline in The New York Times.

1:17:58.541 --> 1:17:59.541
