1:18:01.208 --> 1:18:03.208
Oh. No, thank you.

1:18:04.291 --> 1:18:06.791
-(phones ringing)
-(heavy, indistinct chatter)

1:18:06.875 --> 1:18:08.875
(typewriter keys clacking)

1:18:16.583 --> 1:18:18.041
(chuckles)

1:18:18.125 --> 1:18:19.541
Dad owns the firm.

1:18:19.625 --> 1:18:21.416
Brothers are partners.

1:18:21.500 --> 1:18:22.750
Sooner or later, it's gonna...

1:18:22.833 --> 1:18:24.750
-Lucky Sperm Club.
-Lucky Sperm Club.

