1:20:29.583 --> 1:20:31.000
Probably not.

1:20:31.083 --> 1:20:35.375
I think you should go back to sleep,
wake up in 20 years,

1:20:35.458 --> 1:20:37.833
tell everybody how good you could've been.

1:20:40.125 --> 1:20:41.750
That's what I think.

1:20:43.083 --> 1:20:44.625
-Fuck you.
-Fuck you...

1:20:44.708 --> 1:20:46.375
(inhales sharply)

1:20:46.458 --> 1:20:48.458
(birds chirping)

1:20:51.500 --> 1:20:53.166
(groans softly)

1:20:55.583 --> 1:20:58.083
-(heavy, indistinct chatter)
-(typewriter keys clacking)

1:20:58.166 --> 1:21:00.166
(phones ringing)

1:21:09.708 --> 1:21:11.375
Stinky.

1:21:12.416 --> 1:21:15.250
Hey. He's looking for you.

1:21:16.708 --> 1:21:18.625
(sighs) This is it.

1:21:18.708 --> 1:21:20.083
Lucky bastard.

1:21:23.500 --> 1:21:25.583
As you know,
the editors have had a chance

1:21:25.666 --> 1:21:29.291
to carefully review your work,
and, um, it's terrific.

1:21:29.375 --> 1:21:32.875
Truly, some of your pieces
have been outstanding.

1:21:32.958 --> 1:21:36.708
Though most of them are about, uh,
people in bars on Long Island, uh...

1:21:36.791 --> 1:21:38.125
(both chuckle)

1:21:38.208 --> 1:21:41.291
Uh, some of your pieces have been
truly, truly outstanding.

1:21:41.375 --> 1:21:45.000
Um, that's why I wish I had better news.

1:21:45.083 --> 1:21:47.708
Um, as you know, um,

1:21:47.791 --> 1:21:51.000
when the committee meets
to consider a trainee,

1:21:51.083 --> 1:21:54.041
some editors voice support, some do not.

1:21:54.125 --> 1:21:58.208
A vote's taken-- and, um,
I can't tell you who voted how or why--

1:21:58.291 --> 1:22:00.791
but, um, the end result is

1:22:00.875 --> 1:22:04.000
I cannot offer you
a position as a reporter.

1:22:08.333 --> 1:22:09.750
Thank you.

1:22:09.833 --> 1:22:13.291
The feeling is that you lack,
uh, experience, you know?

1:22:13.375 --> 1:22:16.208
Smaller newspaper, perhaps, you know?

1:22:16.291 --> 1:22:19.958
Someplace where you can, uh,
learn and grow.

1:22:21.791 --> 1:22:23.500
No. Thank you.

1:22:26.625 --> 1:22:28.750
-(phones ringing)
-(heavy, indistinct chatter)

1:22:28.833 --> 1:22:30.833
(typewriter keys clacking)

1:22:47.583 --> 1:22:49.208
