1:23:07.625 --> 1:23:09.958
Okay. You sure you're all right?

1:23:10.041 --> 1:23:12.333
Yeah, I'm fine.

1:23:12.416 --> 1:23:15.125
Good. Be out of here in a few days.

1:23:16.208 --> 1:23:18.083
(sighs)

1:23:18.166 --> 1:23:20.541
What's going on? What's up?

1:23:20.625 --> 1:23:22.208
Ah.

1:23:22.291 --> 1:23:26.000
Well, they didn't offer me that position.

1:23:27.291 --> 1:23:29.375
Pure gold.

1:23:29.458 --> 1:23:31.458
All those assholes are now characters.

1:23:31.541 --> 1:23:32.833
Yeah, I guess so.

