1:23:39.416 --> 1:23:42.750
Maybe... maybe this is the point where

1:23:42.833 --> 1:23:45.291
you tell me something really important.

1:23:45.375 --> 1:23:47.000
Yeah.

1:23:48.416 --> 1:23:52.791
I... To be honest, I'm not 100% sure
we should go memoir.

1:23:52.875 --> 1:23:55.583
But we have to be conscious
of the trend, right?

1:23:56.791 --> 1:23:59.250
However, if it is a memoir,

1:23:59.333 --> 1:24:01.916
and if it's gonna have any structure...

1:24:03.041 --> 1:24:04.958
...you know what you have to do.

